    "Table 7, \"Integrated CNN + DWT + SVM Ensemble Model, \" displays the outcomes.",
    "Table 7 shows the significant improvement in the classification metrics in the final phase of the PolynetDWTCADx model, validating the integration results of SVM with CNN and DWT.",
    "The RV-22 + DWT + SVM and DEV-22 + DWT + SVM models achieved approximately 94.5% and 95% of the training accuracy, respectively.",
    "This suggests that the models effectively learn from the augmented features extracted by CNNs and DWTs.",
    "Additionally, the validation and testing accuracies are satisfactory."
